OL,3,CGB News presenter Eamonn Holmes
OL,4,Crecovering in hospital after stroke
OL,6,FGB News presenter Eamonn Holmes is
OL,7,Frecovering in hospital following a
OL,8,Fstroke, the broadcaster has said.
OL,10,F"Eamonn was taken ill last week, and
OL,11,Fit was later confirmed he had suffered
OL,12,Fa stroke," a GB News spokesperson said.
OL,14,F"He is currently responding well to
OL,15,Ftreatment.
OL,26,@rD@AOUtD@JO]vD@AOU
