OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1775931065
OL,3,CGB News presenter Eamonn Holmes
OL,4,Crecovering in hospital after stroke
OL,6,F"Eamonn has asked for privacy as he
OL,7,Ffocuses on getting better. His
OL,8,Fcolleagues and everyone at GB News
OL,9,Fwish him a speedy recovery and look
OL,10,Fforward to welcoming him back to the
OL,11,FPeople's Channel when he is ready to
OL,12,Freturn."
OL,14,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,15,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,16,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,17,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,19,FThe Northern Irish broadcaster
OL,20,Fpresents GB News Breakfast with his co-
OL,21,Fhost Ellie Costello.
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@HO]
