OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1775931065
OL,3,CGB News presenter Eamonn Holmes
OL,4,Crecovering in hospital after stroke
OL,6,FAlex Armstrong will step in to present
OL,7,Fin his absence this week, the
OL,8,Fbroadcaster added.
OL,10,FAngelos Frangopoulos, chief executive
OL,11,Fof GB News, said: "Eamonn is a loved
OL,12,Fmember of the GB News family, and
OL,13,Fwe're with him every step of the way
OL,14,Fas he recovers."
OL,16,FHolmes has long battled issues after
OL,17,Fdislodging discs in his back, which he
OL,18,Fsaid previously impinged on his
OL,19,Fsciatic nerve and affected the
OL,20,Fmobility of his right leg.
OL,26,@sD@SOUvD@PO]
