OL,3,CGB News presenter Eamonn Holmes
OL,4,Crecovering in hospital after stroke
OL,6,FHe previously spoke about going
OL,7,Fthrough spinal surgery, a double hip
OL,8,Freplacement, and his struggles walking
OL,9,Fand using a mobility scooter.
OL,11,FHolmes had a couple of falls in May
OL,12,Flast year, which seemed to have taken
OL,13,Fplace only weeks apart.
OL,15,FThe former This Morning host was taken
OL,16,Fto hospital after a first fall at his
OL,17,Fhome, then fell from his chair live on-
OL,18,Fair.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/5
